name: Add prospects to Woodpecker from Google Sheets spreadsheet
description: Every time there is a record in a specified Google Sheets spreadsheet, Make will automatically create a prospect in Woodpecker. The template uses this [example spreadsheet](https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1qL1GEV8syciqoeV45sHLXyKt9--R6BfuUOzTLotR06s/edit?usp=sharing).
